We had the chance to talk with Geoff Stacey and his team at Bellator Real Estate & Development. Find out about the company's history, current goals, and how they are helping their agents grow their businesses and save time with Delta Media Group's automated tools by watching this video! https://lnkd.in/eHKcycHU #realestatetechnology #realestatemarketing #realestatesuccess

May shaped up to be the busiest month of the year yet, with record-breaking transactions! 🚀 Commercial rentals stole the show, with offices leading at a remarkable 77% of total commercial transactions. A big shoutout to our sales manager, Mohamed Elsayed, for walking us through the May Market Report during today’s meeting. Stay tuned for our monthly market review. #HamptonsDXB #Hamptons #DubaiRealEstate #RealEstate #MayMadness #RecordBreaking #MarketMovers #CommercialTransactions #RealEstateTrends #MarketInsights

It's been a whirlwind of productivity and success, leading to a whopping 59% increase in business compared to last year! 🚀 As we dive into Q2, I'm pumped to keep up the pace and even accelerate it.
